{"type":"message-part","messageId":"33bd5971-9988-40a5-84bf-f5a5574d2df0","role":"user","index":0,"part":{"type":"text","text":"# Preserving your work\n\nSave a copy of files you create during this task to `/logs/artifacts/`. This directory is preserved after the run so outputs can be inspected. Organize with subdirectories if helpful (e.g., `/logs/artifacts/code/`, `/logs/artifacts/reports/`). The directory already exists and is writable.\n\n---\n\n# Create a Windmill Flow with an Approval (Suspend) Step\n\n## Background\n\nWindmill supports human-in-the-loop workflows via `suspend` modules. A suspend step pauses the flow until a human approves or rejects the continuation. This is essential for high-stakes automated actions — deployments, budget approvals, data deletions — where a human must sign off before the flow proceeds.\n\n## Requirements\n\nCreate two TypeScript scripts and a flow with an approval step between them:\n\n### Script 1: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/prepare_deployment.ts`\n```typescript\nexport async function main(service: string, version: string, environment: string) {\n  return {\n    service,\n    version,\n    environment,\n    deploy_command: `kubectl set image deployment/${service} ${service}=${service}:${version} -n ${environment}`,\n    requires_approval: true\n  };\n}\n```\nMetadata: `summary: \"Prepare a deployment plan\"`, `language: typescript`\n\n### Script 2: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/scripts/execute_deployment.ts`\n```typescript\nexport async function main(deploy_command: string, approved: boolean = true) {\n  if (!approved) {\n    return { status: \"cancelled\", message: \"Deployment was not approved\" };\n  }\n  return { status: \"deployed\", command_run: deploy_command, deployed_at: new Date().toISOString() };\n}\n```\nMetadata: `summary: \"Execute a deployment after approval\"`, `language: typescript`\n\n### Flow: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/flows/deploy_with_approval.yaml`\n```yaml\nsummary: \"Deploy a service with human approval\"\nvalue:\n  modules:\n    - id: prepare\n      value:\n        type: script\n        path: f/scripts/prepare_deployment\n        input_transforms:\n          service:\n            type: static\n            value: \"api-server\"\n          version:\n            type: static\n            value: \"v1.2.3\"\n          environment:\n            type: static\n            value: \"production\"\n    - id: approval\n      value:\n        type: flow\n        path: hub/0/approval\n        input_transforms: {}\n    - id: deploy\n      value:\n        type: script\n        path: f/scripts/execute_deployment\n        input_transforms:\n          deploy_command:\n            type: javascript\n            expr: \"results.prepare.deploy_command\"\n```\n\n## Constraints\n\n- Project path: `/home/user/windmill-project`\n- Flow file: `/home/user/windmill-project/f/flows/deploy_with_approval.yaml`\n- The approval step must use `path: hub/0/approval`\n- Step ids must be `prepare`, `approval`, `deploy`\n\n## Integrations\n\nNone."}}
